---
import Leadership from "../../layouts/Leadership.astro";
---

<Leadership
  title="Coaching-Angebote — Leadership Coaching | Marcus Eichler"
  description="Karriere-Kompass, Führungs-Coaching und Executive Coaching. Alle Angebote im Überblick."
  path="/leadership/angebote"
>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0A1628 0%, #015FA3 100%); color: #FFFFFF; padding: 4rem 1rem 3rem; text-align: center;">
    <div style="max-width: 42rem; margin: 0 auto;">
      <p style="font-size: 0.8125rem; font-weight: 700; color: #93C5FD; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Alle Angebote</p>
      <h1 style="font-size: 2.25rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
        Dein Weg — dein Tempo — dein Coaching
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size: 1rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); line-height: 1.7;">
        Alle Preise auf Anfrage. Wir klären im kostenlosen Erstgespräch, was zu dir und deiner Situation passt.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Angebote Detail -->
  <section style="background-color: #FFFFFF; padding: 4rem 1rem;">
    <div style="max-width: 56rem; margin: 0 auto; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 3rem;">

      <!-- Karriere-Kompass -->
      <div id="kompass" style="border-radius: 1rem; border: 2px solid #DBEAFE; padding: 2.5rem; scroll-margin-top: 5rem;">
        <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 2rem; align-items: flex-start;">
          <div style="flex: 1; min-width: 260px;">
            <p style="font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700; color: #015FA3; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Einstieg</p>
            <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 800; color: #0A1628; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Karriere-Kompass</h2>
            <p style="font-size: 1rem; color: #374151; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
              Eine intensive Session, in der wir gemeinsam Klarheit schaffen: Wo stehst du wirklich? Was hält dich zurück? Welche konkreten nächsten Schritte bringen dich ans Ziel?
            </p>
            <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0 0 1.5rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem;">
              <li style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.9375rem; color: #374151;"><span style="color: #015FA3; font-weight: 700;">✓</span> 1 Session à 90 Minuten (online)</li>
              <li style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.9375rem; color: #374151;"><span style="color: #015FA3; font-weight: 700;">✓</span> Ehrliche Standortanalyse deiner Karriere</li>
              <li style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.9375rem; color: #374151;"><span style="color: #015FA3; font-weight: 700;">✓</span> Konkreter Aktionsplan mit 3 nächsten Schritten</li>
              <li style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.9375rem; color: #374151;"><span style="color: #015FA3; font-weight: 700;">✓</span> Schriftliche Zusammenfassung im Nachgang</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="https://tidycal.com/marcuseichler/kennenlerngesprach-mit-marcus-eichler-1wr7yd6" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
              style="display: inline-block; background-color: #015FA3; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: 700; padding: 0.875rem 1.75rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9375rem;">
              Gespräch buchen →
            </a>
          </div>
          <div style="background-color: #EFF6FF; border-radius: 0.75rem; padding: 1.5rem; min-width: 180px; text-align: center;">
            <p style="font-size: 0.8125rem; color: #6B7280; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">Investition</p>
            <p style="font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 800; color: #015FA3; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">Auf Anfrage</p>
            <p style="font-size: 0.8125rem; color: #6B7280;">einmalig</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Führungs-Coaching -->
      <div id="coaching" style="border-radius: 1rem; border: 2px solid #015FA3; background-color: #F8FAFF; padding: 2.5rem; position: relative; scroll-margin-top: 5rem;">
        <span style="position: absolute; top: -0.75rem; left: 1.5rem; background-color: #015FA3; color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700; padding: 0.2rem 0.75rem; border-radius: 9999px;">Beliebt</span>
        <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 2rem; align-items: flex-start;">
          <div style="flex: 1; min-width: 260px;">
            <p style="font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700; color: #015FA3; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Begleitung · 3 Monate</p>
            <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 800; color: #0A1628; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Führungs-Coaching</h2>
            <p style="font-size: 1rem; color: #374151; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
              Drei Monate intensiver Begleitung, in denen wir deinen nächsten Karriereschritt gemeinsam planen und umsetzen — oder deine neue Führungsrolle auf ein stabiles Fundament stellen.
            </p>
            <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0 0 1.5rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem;">
              <li style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.9375rem; color: #374151;"><span style="color: #015FA3; font-weight: 700;">✓</span> 12 Coaching-Sessions (wöchentlich, 60 Min.)</li>
              <li style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.9375rem; color: #374151;"><span style="color: #015FA3; font-weight: 700;">✓</span> Zwischen-Sessions erreichbar per Nachricht</li>
              <li style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.9375rem; color: #374151;"><span style="color: #015FA3; font-weight: 700;">✓</span> Karriere-Roadmap & Positionierungsstrategie</li>
              <li style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.9375rem; color: #374151;"><span style="color: #015FA3; font-weight: 700;">✓</span> Feedback zu konkreten Situationen (Gespräche, Verhandlungen)</li>
              <li style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.9375rem; color: #374151;"><span style="color: #015FA3; font-weight: 700;">✓</span> Abschluss-Session: Nächste 6 Monate planen</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="https://tidycal.com/marcuseichler/kennenlerngesprach-mit-marcus-eichler-1wr7yd6" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
              style="display: inline-block; background-color: #015FA3; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: 700; padding: 0.875rem 1.75rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9375rem;">
              Erstgespräch buchen →
            </a>
          </div>
          <div style="background-color: #EFF6FF; border-radius: 0.75rem; padding: 1.5rem; min-width: 180px; text-align: center;">
            <p style="font-size: 0.8125rem; color: #6B7280; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">Investition</p>
            <p style="font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 800; color: #015FA3; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">Auf Anfrage</p>
            <p style="font-size: 0.8125rem; color: #6B7280;">3 Monate</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Executive Coaching -->
      <div id="executive" style="border-radius: 1rem; border: 2px solid #DBEAFE; padding: 2.5rem; scroll-margin-top: 5rem;">
        <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 2rem; align-items: flex-start;">
          <div style="flex: 1; min-width: 260px;">
            <p style="font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700; color: #015FA3; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Intensiv · 6 Monate</p>
            <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 800; color: #0A1628; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Executive Coaching</h2>
            <p style="font-size: 1rem; color: #374151; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
              Für Manager, die den Sprung ins C-Level anstreben, ein eigenes Unternehmen aufbauen oder eine komplexe Transformation verantworten. Sechs Monate strategische Begleitung.
            </p>
            <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0 0 1.5rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem;">
              <li style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.9375rem; color: #374151;"><span style="color: #015FA3; font-weight: 700;">✓</span> Alle Leistungen des Führungs-Coachings</li>
              <li style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.9375rem; color: #374151;"><span style="color: #015FA3; font-weight: 700;">✓</span> Bi-weekly Deep-Dive Sessions (90 Min.)</li>
              <li style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.9375rem; color: #374151;"><span style="color: #015FA3; font-weight: 700;">✓</span> Persönliche Branding-Strategie & LinkedIn-Aufbau</li>
              <li style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.9375rem; color: #374151;"><span style="color: #015FA3; font-weight: 700;">✓</span> Netzwerk-Strategie & Stakeholder-Management</li>
              <li style="display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.9375rem; color: #374151;"><span style="color: #015FA3; font-weight: 700;">✓</span> Prioritärer Zugang zwischen Sessions</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="https://tidycal.com/marcuseichler/kennenlerngesprach-mit-marcus-eichler-1wr7yd6" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
              style="display: inline-block; background-color: #015FA3; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: 700; padding: 0.875rem 1.75rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9375rem;">
              Erstgespräch buchen →
            </a>
          </div>
          <div style="background-color: #EFF6FF; border-radius: 0.75rem; padding: 1.5rem; min-width: 180px; text-align: center;">
            <p style="font-size: 0.8125rem; color: #6B7280; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">Investition</p>
            <p style="font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 800; color: #015FA3; margin-bottom: 0.25rem;">Auf Anfrage</p>
            <p style="font-size: 0.8125rem; color: #6B7280;">6 Monate</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #015FA3 0%, #0A1628 100%); padding: 4rem 1rem; text-align: center;">
    <div style="max-width: 42rem; margin: 0 auto;">
      <h2 style="font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 800; color: #FFFFFF; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">
        Noch unsicher, was passt?
      </h2>
      <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 1.6;">
        Im kostenlosen Erstgespräch finden wir gemeinsam heraus, welches Format am besten zu deiner Situation passt.
      </p>
      <a href="https://tidycal.com/marcuseichler/kennenlerngesprach-mit-marcus-eichler-1wr7yd6" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
        style="display: inline-block; background-color: #FFFFFF; color: #015FA3; font-weight: 700; padding: 1rem 2.5rem; border-radius: 0.5rem; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1rem;">
        Kostenloses Erstgespräch buchen →
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Leadership>
